    faq3_q: "How long does a typical project take?", faq3_a: "Small automations: 1–2 weeks. CRM setup: 2–4 weeks. ERPNext implementation: from 3 months. Every project starts with a clear timeline — no surprises.",
    faq4_q: "What's the advantage of ERPNext over SAP?", faq4_a: "ERPNext is open source — no license fees, no vendor lock-in, your data belongs to you. Full functionality for SMEs: accounting, purchasing, warehouse, HR, e-invoice — without SAP prices and without overengineering.",
    faq5_q: "Do you also work remotely or only in Hamburg?", faq5_a: "I work remotely nationwide and across Europe — most projects are handled entirely online. For companies in Hamburg and the Elmshorn region I'm also available in person on request.",
